# DBTITLE 1,Silver Layer
# MAGIC %md
# MAGIC ## 🥈 Silver Layer: Cleaned & Enriched Data
# MAGIC
# MAGIC **Objective**: Join related tables, apply data quality rules, and create analytics-ready datasets.
# MAGIC
# MAGIC **Transformations**:
# MAGIC - **Joins**: Combine fact tables with dimension tables (products + categories + brands, customers + types + addresses, orders + items + payments)
# MAGIC - **Filtering**: Remove inactive products, validate records
# MAGIC - **Enrichment**: Add calculated fields (e.g., `is_correct` flag for customer validation)
# MAGIC - **Cleanup**: Exclude `_rescued_data` column from final tables
# MAGIC
# MAGIC **Tables Created**: 
# MAGIC - `product_silver` - Products with category and brand names
# MAGIC - `customer_silver` - Customers with type and location
# MAGIC - `order_silver` - Orders with line items and payment amounts
# MAGIC - `payment_silver` - Payments with method names

